data.oai_dc:dc: SUPPLEMENTARY MATERIALS S2. – Set of Euler/X toolkit output Maximally Informative Relations (MIR) for the input data files provided in the Supplementary Materials S1 and for the entire Prim-UC ("primates-all.csv"). Each output file is saved in .csv format. The MIR files form the basis for analyses of name:meaning relations (Tables 3–5).
